{"tid":321949,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【DQ四議員】非建制派補選至少失2席 失分組點票否決權","createTime":"2017-07-14T13:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-16T14:29:56.000Z","uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf47a6dde1e5341b19ca9cdf255e8e8efed35e91","tid":321949,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"【DQ四議員】非建制派補選至少失2席 失分組點票否決權<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170714/large/1500036785_71a6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170714%2Flarge%2F1500036785_71a6.png&h=77328a36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎被政府褫奪立法會議員資格後，法庭再裁定政府司法覆核勝訴，認為羅冠聰、劉小麗、梁國雄及姚松炎的宣誓不合規格，宣佈由去年10月12日宣誓當日起計，4人議席失效，若上訴失敗，便有6席要補選。科大社會學部副教授成名預計，建制派在九西及新東應最少奪2席，地區直選議席將增至18席，相反非建制派會減至17席，喪失在分組點票時的否決權。<br />\n<br />\n他分析，在九西及新東的兩大選區，建制派必然會派人參選，即使泛民派代表出戰補選，在比例代表制下，估計建制派會在九西及新東取得最少2席。而只有1席出缺的港島區，將按單議席單票制補選，估計對非建制派有利。<br />\n<br />\n至於非建制派能否有策略可全奪回6席，他稱，「我覺得係悲觀」，因在比例代表制下，建制派有一定核心的支持者，即鐵票，認為非建制派「無可能6席贏返晒返來」。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&d=AV8D4jVDMEaXT1H5LwPgJdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=b4c9266e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56957050%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170714&h=5dd843a4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56957050&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170714</a>"},{"pid":"d9959a5ea43e79bea73829f55f99e3243e9c18c7","tid":321949,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"咁都要專家，有腦都知啦on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3364994a59b9370057fb0e10ca7b6a7033f0db6","tid":321949,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:10:44.000Z","msg":"可能全軍覆沒"},{"pid":"f02dcc0dd1b183ab3b7f8cda18b5d87660b0a1e1","tid":321949,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T13:11:40.000Z","msg":"等睇蟲蟲被DQ"},{"pid":"e10fc7222e473c153ccf11eb6176eeba0bbf5870","tid":321949,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f637caa23e56214cc4e2897cf9d0cf598e9bb9","tid":321949,"uid":104941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:10:36.000Z","msg":"泛民唔玩五區公投？<br />\n咁保皇狗咪會唔派人選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b88594ec158a647d84b1cd3a18103005d65f13","tid":321949,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:17:01.000Z","msg":"想知現在夠唔夠2/3DQ蟲太"},{"pid":"ba1a004d4435e9ece91c7829828a297d5eee4355","tid":321949,"uid":101909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:21:04.000Z","msg":"應該淨係可以之前無投過票同投左比人DQ果幾個既選民先可以投補選<br />\n1個選民淨係可以投一個人代表自己，如果佢投果位已經係議會，唔應該再有多一個人再代表佢"},{"pid":"d5b28c2ceb7b14c38f78c0d819e118a43c823f86","tid":321949,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T08:23:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e771c9d4d3ca2e0c6c319f587c9ff729b2fae360","tid":321949,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T14:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}